---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About ROSCO S&R | Perth Strip Out & Removal Specialists"
  description="Learn about ROSCO S&R — Perth's trusted specialist in non-structural demolition, strip outs, bathroom and kitchen removal, and surface preparation. Professional, reliable, and experienced."
>
  <section class="bg-bg-base py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:items-start">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none">
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl text-primary">
            About ROSCO S&R
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 text-text-body">
            <p>
              At ROSCO S&R, we specialize in meticulous strip outs, focusing on
              careful removal to preserve the integrity of your fixtures and
              furniture. We understand the value of your assets, so we work with
              the utmost precision to ensure everything is removed respectfully
              and intact.
            </p>
            <p>
              Need to clear some space? Whether it's removing old pergolas,
              decks, or any outdoor structures, we handle it with precision and
              care. We'll leave your outdoor area clean and ready for your next
              project. Ready to transform your space in Perth? Send us a DM for
              a free quote! 📞
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-10 flex gap-x-6">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="rounded-md px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary-hover focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-primary">
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-surface-alt shadow-xl ring-1 ring-border">
          <img
            src="https://ik.imagekit.io/137/rosco-sr/9.webp"
            alt="ROSCO S&R team at work"
            class="h-auto w-full object-contain"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>